  <titles>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Decennial Census Improvement Act of 1987</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">A bill to amend title 13, United States Code, to remedy the historic undercount of the poor and minorities in the decennial census of population and to otherwise improve the overall accuracy of the population data collected in the decennial census by directing the use of appropriate statistical adjustment procedures, and for other purposes.</title>
  </titles>
